================================================================================
Provenance
================================================================================

bsv_third_entry is an extraction/recomposition of the on-chain orchestration
layer from the upstream bonsai-notarized-bitnet project (Apache-2.0). It drives
the separately-licensed chain_c CLIs to publish a receipt's Bitcoin SV "Third
Entry" and to run the AgentTea identity lifecycle.

================================================================================
Third-party components
================================================================================

bsv_third_entry vendors no third-party code. Its runtime is the Python standard
library; it shells out to the chain_c binaries (which carry their own license and
NOTICE). Any development/test-only dependencies are declared in requirements*.txt
and are not redistributed here.
